OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,FMs Smith succeeds as the youngest ever
OL,7,Flife peer Baroness Owen of Alderley
OL,8,FEdge, who was made a life peer in July
OL,9,F2023 at the age of 30.
OL,11,FLlanfaes is a small village in Ynys
OL,12,FMon where she grew up and she chose
OL,13,Fthe title to "shine a light on the
OL,14,Fexperiences of people in areas like
OL,15,Fmine".
