OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,FAhead of her introduction to the House
OL,7,Fof Lords, Ms Smith said: "As I am
OL,8,Fintroduced to the House of Lords as
OL,9,Fits youngest member today, I will be
OL,10,Facutely aware of the unique
OL,11,Fresponsibility I hold to be a voice
OL,12,Ffor my generation.
OL,14,F"We came of age amidst the global
OL,15,Frecession and austerity, seeing the
OL,16,Fdecimation of youth services and the
OL,17,Fgrowing mental health crisis.
