OL,3,CYoungest ever life peer to take her
OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,F"Against the backdrop of looming
OL,7,Fclimate catastrophe, we face stark
OL,8,Fwealth disparities, soaring debts,
OL,9,Funaffordable housing, and precarious
OL,10,Femployment. We are incensed by the
OL,11,Finjustices suffered by so many in our
OL,12,Fsociety.
OL,14,F"As a young carer to my late father, I
OL,15,Fexperienced the kind of struggles that
OL,16,Fso many people face every day ` the
OL,17,Fsame barriers, the same prejudices.
