OL,3,CYoungest ever life peer to take her
OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,F"As someone who grew up in a rural,
OL,7,Funderprivileged area, I experienced
OL,8,Fthe lack of connectedness, lack of
OL,9,Finfrastructure, that so many of our
OL,10,Fcommunities still face.
OL,12,F"I chose 'Llanfaes' as my title as I
OL,13,Fwanted to send a message. I wanted to
OL,14,Fshine a light on the experiences of
OL,15,Fpeople in areas like mine.
OL,17,F"My experiences are far from unique,
OL,18,Fbut are a world away from the reality
OL,19,Flived by most in Westminster.
