OL,3,CYoungest ever life peer to take her
OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,F"Across Wales, young voices are
OL,7,Fdrowned out by the failures of the
OL,8,FUK's political and economic
OL,9,Fstructures. They deserve to be heard.
OL,11,F"In a House of Lords where not many
OL,12,Fmembers will look like me, I know that
OL,13,FI will have to shout loudly. I'm ready
OL,14,Ffor that."
OL,16,FMs Smith studied law at Bangor
OL,17,FUniversity for one year before leaving
OL,18,Fher studies to campaign to become NUS
OL,19,FWales deputy president in 2016.
