OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,FAt 25, she became chief of staff to
OL,7,Fthe Plaid Senedd group and has
OL,8,Fcampaigned on issues such as widening
OL,9,Faccess into education, the right to
OL,10,Fself-determination, and tackling
OL,11,Fpoverty.
OL,13,FLord Wigley, Plaid's honorary
OL,14,Fpresident, said he planned to retire
OL,15,Ffrom the House of Lords at the next
OL,16,Fgeneral election as he turns 81 in
OL,17,FApril.
