OL,6,F"It is true that I have indicated in
OL,7,Fthe past that I did not foresee myself
OL,8,Fcontinuing in the Lords beyond the age
OL,9,Fof 80," he said.
OL,11,F"However, with Carmen's very welcome
OL,12,Fappointment, I resolved to stay a
OL,13,Flittle longer to help her settle into
OL,14,Fthe work.
