OL,4,Cseat in Lords
OL,6,F"I very much hope that during this
OL,7,Fperiod, Plaid Cymru's other nominee,
OL,8,FRt Hon Elfyn Llwyd, former
OL,9,Fparliamentary leader, will be
OL,10,Fappointed to the Lords ` and that this
OL,11,Fwill deliver on the earlier commitment
OL,12,Fthat Plaid Cymru will have three seats
OL,13,Fin the second chamber, to work for
OL,14,FWales to the best of our endeavours.
OL,16,F"In the meantime, I look forward to
OL,17,Fworking alongside Carmen Smith and
OL,18,Fwish her every success."
